Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.36,0:00:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由小薰提案的「我们的展览」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.10,0:00:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们作为毫无特色的普通高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像淡蓝色车票一样  没有目的地般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飘忽不定的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想都没想过能够做成这般大事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起在考虑和准备着  积极地加油着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是随着渐渐临近那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是会有些不安  变得紧张起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传单还剩下这点了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.44,0:00:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发了很多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海报也只有一点了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贴在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有我们忘记的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有忘记贴的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.98,0:00:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.06,0:01:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我们的展览」  天妇罗是濑户内产的康吉鳗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天我就在市内转转  帮你们宣传啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是为我们着想吗  还是故意找茬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.56,0:01:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个难题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们要办展览吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.46,0:01:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.34,0:01:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下传单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:23.30,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(480,105)\fad(500,500)}「因为又是新的一年」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上到11点了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没有过的紧张感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正式开展！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有一个人过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是才刚开始嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天气又冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小町妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事小鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有人来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:04:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  别那么慌张嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一名哦  慢慢欣赏…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  选照片花了我不少工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我一起出展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小町的照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想临时加入吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  能展览的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在香君的旁边或者下面怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话也许可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不介意哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你的企图吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就按这感觉来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得热闹起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这里面拍得好像都是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与香君温馨的画形成对比  是赤裸裸的暴力照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  说别人的脸是暴力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第一位客人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光…临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是再好不过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一名好像已经被占了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也发生了好多事情  真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用那个相机拍的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我一直带在身上的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这幅画是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肉球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面的照片是我拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做熏香好像很难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下我来现场制作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎欢迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这照片是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这画的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肉球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面有标题的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很棒  心里变得温暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干燥的时间差不多是在白炽灯下放一周
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:51.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}理疗系  放松精神系 清爽系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好干燥会长虫的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰  真是是盛况空前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈不能来真是遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也可以不必勉强的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是薰做的杨树吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是熏香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪惠  这个超好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有这么厉害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能选择装饰配品真好啊  你们觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大好评呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  多亏了您的多方协助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为纪惠很努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我只是借给你厨房而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起晚了  一生的失败
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是HOBORO店主啊  真是奇遇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇遇？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之后有樱田同学的朗读剧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话就和我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  说定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:51.37,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}樱田麻音  竹笋的妖精  小笋的危险冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:08:01.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}加油  虽然很想去给你应援  因为没办法  就在这里应援吧  \N麻音的待客之心一定能为大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:08:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记鞠躬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是竹笋的妖精小笋的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笋是个容易害羞的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笋  出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算叫她  他也不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笋  美丽的鲜花开放了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闻起来很香的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有好吃的蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:08:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笋  出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笋出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笋？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家一起叫她哦  1…2…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笋～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笋笋～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香君  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了大家  小笋出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笋遇到了很…很糟糕的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲知详情　请待下回分解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有下次？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这幅画是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肉球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塙学姐  围裙很适合你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娇羞了  好可爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那现在开始我就现场制作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  豆馅配品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的推荐哦  很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  要再来一份了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得有些害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  每一张都是好照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一阵我看了志保美小姐的工作  就这样想过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志保美小姐的照片是给人观赏的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的则是给自己看的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我就想选一些能让人看后绽放笑容的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家想看怎样的照片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了什么样的照片会绽放笑容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样想着反而更加迷惘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是选了自己想看的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以总觉得让志保美小姐看了好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我觉得泽渡小姐可能还没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你已经得到了很宝贵的东西了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能为今天来看展览的人着想而烦恼的泽渡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经在不知不觉中抓住了非常宝贵的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贵的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一定很快就会注意到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽渡小姐一定能拍下撼动心灵的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是第二章  小笋去了鄂霍次克  开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有装剩了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家写了很多问卷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的有好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  纪惠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这上面写照片很好看呢  小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤裸裸的表情魄力一百分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是说小町啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能有更刺激的熏香  辣椒之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有蛋糕  希望有辣椒配品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么喜欢辣椒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做那种事的话  我会被说拿食物来玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里写竹笋的妖精小笋我全听了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想的故事很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小笋最后被吃掉了很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊  那里我也很犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:13:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是反之结局就很没劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:01.54,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老姐的  有认真写啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰  还有大家  真是很棒的「我们的展览」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们这作为一年结束的最后礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也该准备点什么作为回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔的预告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年一开始似乎就会发生什么的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也写了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明等下直接说给我听就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次好好看了小薰喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你不怎么说自己的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你教大家做法的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有作为中心开展了这个展览的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都使我无比高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来等下要向你妈妈去炫耀一番了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很棒的展览会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年还要继续办哦　我很期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得办这样的活动很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也想办一个试试看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想看小笋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪  奶奶写的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个很愉快的展览会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫的照片是你通过照相机的四角小窗  自己所找到的宝物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你给我看了这么美好的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办展览真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你新年顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我跟上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很不错的果断一撞  薰亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就来做示范了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了香亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音亲  做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要倒计时了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也还请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝热甜酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:16:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝好喝的甜酒吗  很热乎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是千寻打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫喵  新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在和大家一起新年参拜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  枫喵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我也去新年参拜  和小智一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我在发贺年短信的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果断邀请了她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次枫喵来我这的时候  一定介绍给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  期待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎在听到枫喵要搬家去竹原的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种寂寞的感觉  已经是假的一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:16:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  我没哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年我也要变得积极起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫喵  今年也多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是请你多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年参拜后我发照片给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和大家说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说要说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那换她们说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了「我们的展览」的照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵比利他们也出展了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  喵比利大受好评哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快点换给我啊  薰亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上5点  群发短信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐代美姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy new year
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得她好有干劲的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为从「我们的展览」那得到了大家的美妙的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照约定我来回礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个我可以拒绝吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦  不要客气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火有好好关掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  话说现在要出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是拿身心来开玩笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰的签是凶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾  是大凶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  因为我的是大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么  就只有老姐没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会超级安全驾驶的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山那里水结冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好驾驶的话  会坠崖的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:18:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结冰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠崖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止都是不安因素啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  去朝日山看新年日出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真会成为不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这路好像错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  导航是骗子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直受您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再拜托您救援吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  大家小心地下车哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下车？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上好滑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山路的话就坠崖了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导航出错反而是好运吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.09,0:19:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰的大凶被我的大吉救了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:19:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我有个好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然其实是要在看日出的时候拿出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里来着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  找到了找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  救援到来之前用这个暖和暖和吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我们是来做什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初日看不成了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是应该去海边的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:20:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始变亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像新年要从小镇那边悄然接近一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到小镇这样的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在山上  这就是看不到的景色了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山被朝日点亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是从山上看不到的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座山一定也不知道自己有多么漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像大家一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在梦想的途中会迷惘和彷徨  可能会无法注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是实际上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论在谁看来都是绚烂夺目的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:21:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在闪闪发光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那座山一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰  帮我拿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一样到来的崭新的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.87,0:22:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天大家要踏上自己的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想留住这个宝贵的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫的照片是你通过照相机的四角小窗  自己所找到的宝物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这句话…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爸爸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这扇窗口里  爸爸看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是爸爸找到的宝物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.83,0:22:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为时光荏苒  会变得无法传达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.98,0:22:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才想留住这些珍贵的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:22:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份感情现在在我心中沉淀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我和爸爸的心连了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么小啪  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.31,0:23:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  今后也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.83,0:23:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.85,0:23:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请你多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.20,0:23:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走错路真是正确啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人这么说还真是让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让她得意忘形  薰亲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许叫我薰亲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.51,0:23:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  打扰您了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.93,0:23:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车子滑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.70,0:23:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很冷的吧  我现在去拿点热东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.43,0:24:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到电话说  有车子打滑了  女孩们很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿了这个来  救援来之前你们先取暖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.56,0:24:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  把这个吃了暖暖身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.89,0:24:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得寒冷的早晨变得温暖起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.87,0:24:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在眼前的宝物可能随着时光流逝会渐渐消失
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.66,0:24:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用爸爸留给我的照片拍下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论何时都能讲述这些宝贵的瞬间的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.32,0:24:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
